{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_017pED38DqRFTmuuubAjpzWa","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Audit Module\n     2→\n     3→Compliance audit coordinator. Checks all dimensions (observability, testing, documentation, verification, infrastructure) and reports project health.\n     4→\n     5→## Files\n     6→\n     7→- `types.ts` — DimensionStatus, DimensionResult, AuditGap, AuditResult type definitions\n     8→- `dimensions.ts` — Per-dimension checkers: checkObservability, checkTesting, checkDocumentation, checkVerification, checkInfrastructure\n     9→- `index.ts` — Barrel exports + runAudit coordinator that calls all dimension checkers\n    10→- `report.ts` — formatAuditHuman (UX prefix format) and formatAuditJson (structured output)\n    11→\n    12→## Key Patterns\n    13→\n    14→- Coordinator pattern: runAudit calls 5 dimension checkers, collects results, computes overall status\n    15→- Each dimension checker wraps an existing module function and maps output to DimensionResult\n    16→- Result<T> discriminated union for error handling — never throws\n    17→- Graceful degradation: each checker catches its own errors, returns warn/fail instead of crashing\n    18→- Barrel imports only: consumers import from index.ts\n    19→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01KBt1xzNkF45pjf2bZesegY","session_id":"0deb1693-f450-4ee3-ba9f-130c7ba0aec5","uuid":"f29c2159-8e5d-4d4a-86ba-a9a72d1c3971","timestamp":"2026-03-20T09:22:13.252Z"}
