ent to the index-based scheme and would need content-based hashing to fully solve. Acceptable for current scope per story spec.\n\n**Items sent back for re-development:** None. All HIGH and MEDIUM issues were fixed in this review session."}],"totalDurationMs":259558,"totalTokens":66621,"totalToolUseCount":46,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":297,"cache_read_input_tokens":65072,"output_tokens":1251,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":297},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
